        "bug"
      ],
      "body": "The original doc says in the first paragraph of section 3:\r\n```\r\nWG participants should specifically note the\r\nrequirements for disclosure of conflicts of interest in [2].\r\n```\r\n\r\n[2] is RFC 2028, obsoleted by 9281 and neither one of these mentions conflict of interest.\r\n\r\nSee email thread at https://mailarchive.ietf.org/arch/msg/ietf/8mEwZkwtL-WNCPyZ5hBd7FaWVq8/\r\n",
      "createdAt": "2024-08-09T20:26:48Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-10-15T17:49:06Z",
      "closedAt": "2025-10-15T17:49:06Z",
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "richsalz",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "Per email with Scott, this should probably be a reference to 2026 because that talks about disclosures.",
          "createdAt": "2025-04-04T18:42:41Z",
          "updatedAt": "2025-04-04T18:42:41Z"
        }
