      "body": "The section titled \"Internet-Drafts\" has a bunch of outdated information\r\n\r\n- Says to submit via email\r\n- Says secretariat maintains boilerplate\r\n- refers to 1id-organization.txt file\r\n- refers to 1id-guidelines.txt file\r\n",
