              "body": "Presumably, this could be **changed** by mutual agreement of AD+chairs.\r\nThat the choice does not require a charter revision. You say that later on.  \r\nAnd that it does not require the tooling to enforce the choice?\r\nIt seems like a lot words here.\r\n",
              "createdAt": "2025-10-06T22:10:35Z",
              "updatedAt": "2025-10-06T22:10:48Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 84,
              "body": "This requires tooling changes.\r\n(I think that milestones would get used and update more often if WG chairs could do this without supervision)\r\n",
